{"type": "article", "id": 58515, "title": "一块木板分两半，一半是搁架一半是磁性板｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-20T23:07:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 54412, "name": "LAWA DESIGN"}, {"id": 54413, "name": "JOKJOR"}, {"id": 54414, "name": "V & KO"}, {"id": 2629, "name": "HAY"}, {"id": 54415, "name": "Olav van Lede"}, {"id": 54416, "name": "George Sowden"}, {"id": 54417, "name": "Hubert Chan"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 227, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181120194715Iu9xczPEGJj1D2VR.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Twist Shelf by LAWA DESIGN</h3><p>丹麦设计工作室 LAWA DESIGN 的设计师 Allen Shakir 和 Ewa Bryzek 创造了一款多用途的搁架 Twist Shelf，既是搁架，也是磁性板，中部有一个扭转的形态。</p><p>它采用未经处理的橡木制成，原始状态就是一款木板，扭转 90 度后，靠在墙壁上，成为磁性板。</p><p>它可以用于厨房，比如存放香料和展示食谱，也可以用于办公空间，收纳办公用品和便利贴、备忘录等，或者用在玄关位置，收纳钥匙、太阳镜等小物件等等。售价 1999 丹麦克朗（约合人民币 2126 元），<a href=\"https://lawadesign.dk/collections/all/products/twist-shelf\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811201948255c0YNr3tWMBkbzhq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194825Xc82WqN4xFRGSn1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194826jBrvZp5iGW790OQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194826Lo8miNyqwxGAHhWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194827pmVcQBw8IForMDqE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194827OcD0VusbyMiFnoz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Playfully Balanced TWINS Adjustable Mirror Set by Olav van Lede for JOKJOR</h3><p>荷兰设计品牌 JOKJOR 最近发布了一款镜子 TWINS，出自设计师 Olav van Lede 之手。正如其名，TWINS 其实是一对相同的镜子，由一根绳子连接起来，镜子可以悬挂在点状钩子上，允许用户以自己喜欢的方式挂置在墙壁上，也可以成为墙面装饰物。</p><p>用户可以安装一对圆形钢钩，以便根据个人喜好上下移动两个哑光黑色钢镜，高度角度皆可调整。目前，TWINS 有红黑两种棉质绳索可选。售价 249 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.jokjor.com/en/shop/mirror-set/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194856GEfwvk2eAsBOLryj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194856SMWTx7cUfnq8stgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.065625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194856tOrLRpwsYnCyD0f9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194857HeBMCGXkmVW2nhzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.491406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194858t3doNprjHqA04lRk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.460156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Coffee Table by V &amp; KO</h3><p>荷兰设计工作室 V &amp; KO 最近推出了一款色彩明丽的咖啡桌。这款咖啡桌看起来是个具有实用功能的艺术品。咖啡桌由两部分组成，一部分是由彩色几何图形拼接成的盒子，一部分是下方将盒子抬离地面的人手。</p><p>这款咖啡桌让人想起立体派艺术家的原创画作，利用鲜艳明快的色彩挑战观看者的神经。而在盒子形桌面之下还隐藏着让人意想不到的细节，将盒子抬离地面的双手，其实是下方张开双臂的艳黄色男性半身像的一部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194931fle3zbk9rHhj6GA5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.325545\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194933g350FyHxeXWuSBcq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666147\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194933yLxJaplGcgoteR7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585670\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194934QVE0ud5wXgkBjGJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611198\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120194934gNl1GrstAUY7cynj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.468118\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811201949353KqWkEaFCimZSVPe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.579688\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.vkodesign.com/coffeetable\" rel=\"nofollow\">V &amp; KO</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Sowden Water Bottle by George Sowden forHay</h3><p>设计大师 George Sowden 为丹麦设计品牌 HAY 设计的保温杯 Sowden Bottle，单看其玩味用色及形状，可能更像是一件当代摆设，壶身采用上窄下阔的无缝裙装设计，彩色涂层包裹着优质不锈钢内胆，无论冷热饮品都能保温，盖子则采用螺旋设计，绝对密封。</p><p>作为孟菲斯运动标志性的设计师之一，George Sowden 多彩和现代风格的设计语言，与 HAY 的调性完美混搭。售价 39 美元，<a href=\"https://store.wallpaper.com/en/new/w*-editors-picks/hay/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195007jlEZJLpzWHCu3ity.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556701\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195008W15vOgroUCZfpS2j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195009CP0uW9aXx6iMdUYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667123\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MONOS by Hubert Chan</h3><p>MONOS 是一个专门制造优质而简约的行李箱的品牌，专注于质量和细节。每件产品均采用超轻型航空航天级聚碳酸酯制造而成，几乎可以说是具有坚不可摧的质量。</p><p>整个箱子采用哑光的外壳，耐刮擦，能够承受最粗糙的行李搬运工的搬运。它还配有可伸缩的手柄，由高级铝材质制成，定制化的设计则用于让它减少横向运动，而静音运行的 360°车轮则可以让它非常安静地行走。</p><p>用户可以选择登机箱，加大号登机箱以及托运箱等尺寸，以及八种不同的颜色款式。售价 150 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.monos.com/pages/kickstarter\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195039xWjBhu3mwS0lGqOp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195041Cui8S6akOWrUmfeN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195042dKGbYIz3oxg6f0CZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195042IFusyxnpWUJPKXjN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195043QXGRUF8O9HpWzsD7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195044NEO3sJm1vjVg9YR0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181120195044T63cQ8tESUD9lHhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}